{"tid":1885651,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"求助...屋企隻松鼠狗唔知皮膚咩事","createTime":"2020-02-18T12:16:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T03:35:57.000Z","uid":295341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5f62a3b35c86d89e7f002da0c7c196898714686e","tid":1885651,"uid":295341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T12:16:08.000Z","msg":"老豆老母前幾年領養左隻松鼠仔...<br />\n而家10歲, 9月既時候已經咁樣<br />\n唔知咩事係咁甩毛<br />\n去vet 睇完獸醫做body check 驗血驗尿<br />\n佢話好健康冇問題, <br />\nd 毛會生返出黎不過可能要幾個月時間...<br />\n而家過左5個月都仲係咁,<br />\n帶去睇第2個獸醫都係一樣話健康冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢食慾正常, 仲係札札跳好活潑...<br />\n有冇高人可以指點一下應該點做...<br />\n(有用含硫黃精成份既shampoo幫佢沖涼)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fhKEzN9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfhKEzN9.png&h=839b52ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n萬分感激"},{"pid":"c548a27c9653d7f53d0f9fe882fd76d9e01448e5","tid":1885651,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T13:41:46.000Z","msg":"有冇搬屋或者同之前唔一樣生活習慣？會唔會好焦慮？有冇食過TG?"},{"pid":"f1dc67d5ff3f044abefbcfd09209683f87ef7193","tid":1885651,"uid":295341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c548a27c9653d7f53d0f9fe882fd76d9e01448e5","tid":1885651,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T13:41:46.000Z","msg":"有冇搬屋或者同之前唔一樣生活習慣？會唔會好焦慮？有冇食過TG?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:06:21.000Z","msg":"係有搬過屋,但發生呢個情況係搬完屋半年後,<br />\n冇焦慮,就算冇人係屋企佢都係行行企企訓下咁等人返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地係美國,冇食tg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d2c85a07938e2f113bf082476ac9ef04c804d64","tid":1885651,"uid":270830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:37:08.000Z","msg":"影哂成隻嚟睇吓 <br />\n再上網search&quot;庫興氏症&quot;睇吓似唔似"},{"pid":"0b91f76b7e8e2a1a4fcda4709020aaffab46044f","tid":1885651,"uid":295341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d2c85a07938e2f11